entry.title: AhmadSabbirChowdhury/Microsoft-AdventureWorks-Database-Analysis-Visualization-with-PowerBI
entry.summary: I chose 'AdventureWorksLT2019.bak' and 'AdventureWorksLT2017.bak' data for analysis & visualization. The query editing was done in 'Microsoft SQL Server Management Studio' and the visualization part was using 'Microsoft Power BI'. Also for analysis, I used MS Excel and PowerBI's query tool.
